In terms of applications, the retail sector emerges as a key player in driving the growth of the SMS marketing market. Retailers are leveraging SMS marketing to create personalized communication with customers, inform them about promotions, discounts, and new products, ultimately driving sales. Moreover, the BFSI sector, with its increasing focus on secure communication channels for financial transactions, is also expected to drive the demand for SMS marketing solutions to ensure effective customer engagement.

